As a user, I want instructions on how to play the game, so I can play well.

As a user, I want to choose categories, so that I can pick something I know.

As a user, I want the option of seeing the correct answer after I make an incorrect guess, so that I can learn from my mistake

As a user, I want my attempts scored in some manner, so I can compare my results from game to game.

As a user, I want the option to choose levels of difficulty